1
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:06,640
What brings you here?

2
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:09,239
To end your reign

3
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:11,439
of terror on this world.

4
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,640
That ring...

5
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:17,680
Master.

6
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,040
Master,

7
00:01:19,359 --> 00:01:20,519
I have a request.

8
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:21,760
Daozhi,

9
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,239
you've come just in time.

10
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,480
We've finally uncovered

11
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:27,200
clues to the Demon King's transformation.

12
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:37,400
So you've taken another form to survive.

13
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:39,040
Chixin?

14
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,879
After a century,

15
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:45,120
you've actually improved.

16
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,400
That's right.

17
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,159
I am Chixin.

18
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,480
Your incompetence

19
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:52,439
made me rejoice for nothing.

20
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,840
Master,

21
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,400
the most pressing issue now

22
00:01:57,719 --> 00:02:00,040
is not to destroy the Demon Village,

23
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:03,400
but to find a new vessel.

24
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,240
You took the innocent

25
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,319
you took innocent humans' bodies.

26
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,759
Who's the real menace here,

27
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,319
me, a witch,

28
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:54,759
or you, a former auspicious beast?

29
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,159
Cut the crap!

30
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,280
Hand over the Water Cloud Rhinoceros,

31
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:01,560
or I'll leave you nothing but a corpse!

32
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:33,599
Meng Li!

33
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,840
Let's split up.

34
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,719
I'll handle this,

35
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,159
you go deal with the rhinoceros.

36
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,400
The Red Heart fragment in her is fierce.

37
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:40,719
I'm afraid you can't handle it.

38
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,000
I have a way to deal with it.

39
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:43,800
Trust me.

40
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:50,759
Shen Que,

41
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:51,919
after a hundred years,

42
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:53,159
you ruined my plan again.

43
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:55,919
My good disciple,

44
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,360
your kong fu in both lives was taught by me.

45
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,560
You can't beat me.

46
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,000
If I can control you for a moment

47
00:04:01,319 --> 00:04:02,639
by my death,

48
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,159
it's worth it.

49
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:36,720
Wait!

50
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,600
Shen Que,

51
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,800
are you hurt?

52
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:44,879
I'm fine.

53
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,399
What about Chi Xin?

54
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,639
I've defeated him.

55
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,279
He won't come for a while.

56
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,759
I'll sink the Water Cloud Rhinoceros now.

57
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:52,560
No!

58
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,680
A'Li,

59
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,920
leave this to me.

60
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:06,360
What did you call me?

61
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,560
A'Li.

62
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:12,399
Shen Que never called me A'Li after losing his memory.

63
00:06:13,879 --> 00:06:15,519
I heard everyone call you that,

64
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:17,839
so I followed suit.

65
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:23,240
Shattered dreams with lingering affection,

66
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,879
Heaven and Earth overturned,

67
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,759
Profound Amber sinks into the abyss, Calamity's end.

68
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,600
This poem...

69
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,279
Shen Que knows its meaning.

70
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,319
Only I can destroy the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

71
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,439
Who are you?

72
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,600
Kill me,

73
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,519
and you'll be Red Heart.

74
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,160
Meng Li,

75
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,959
I must have the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

76
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:55,759
You are Red Heart?

77
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,120
Just a Dream-Eating Imp.

78
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:39,279
Such a petty trick,

79
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:41,079
yet you dare to harm me.

80
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,800
How ridiculous!

81
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,040
Shen Que,

82
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,759
wake up!

83
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,480
Don't let Red Heart disturb you.

84
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,279
Meng Li,

85
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,879
Run!

86
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,000
Leave here!

87
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:06,399
You two are really affectionate.

88
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,439
So,

89
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,519
you're just going to let go

90
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,439
of what happened a hundred years ago?

91
00:08:12,319 --> 00:08:15,399
You're just a demon in name,

92
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:19,199
so soft and easily fooled.

93
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:20,720
After being seriously injured

94
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,319
and sleeping for a hundred years,

95
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:24,680
you still haven't improved.

96
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:27,439
I really overestimated you.

97
00:08:32,319 --> 00:08:32,959
Meng Li!

98
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,080
Run!

99
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,480
Run!

100
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,759
Mere mortals

101
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,399
dare challenge me?

102
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,240
Now that my soul is whole,

103
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:49,879
no force in this world

104
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:53,240
can stand against me!

105
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,279
Now,

106
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,879
I'll kill you, leader of all demons!

107
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,559
From this moment on,

108
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,200
whether human

109
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,480
or demon,

110
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,960
will be my puppets!

111
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,279
Shen Que!

112
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:16,240
Come on!

113
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,879
Wake up!

114
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:23,559
The moon is bright,

115
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:26,919
the wind is blowing,

116
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,759
the apricot flowers are falling.

117
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,360
I'm lost in memories,

118
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,639
like in a dream.

119
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,320
My tears

120
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,000
are flowing...

121
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,399
Thank you.

122
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:02,960
My name is Meng Li.

123
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,320
You can call me Li.

124
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,840
What's your name?

125
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:15,720
This time, I'll let it go.

126
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,200
If you forget again,

127
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,799
I'll really eat it.

128
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,279
[Li,]

129
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,840
[I, Shen Daozhi,]

130
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,759
[will never let you down.]

131
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,279
[If I do,]

132
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,399
[may I perish.]

133
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,039
[No matter how many lifetimes,]

134
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,039
[my love for you remains.]

135
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,720
[Reuniting with you this life]

136
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,720
[is a blessing beyond measure.]

137
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:49,600
[Aging together can't be replaced.]

138
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,679
[If this is fate's design,]

139
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:56,159
[it's the best ending for us.]

140
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:18,679
A'Li!

141
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:19,799
A'Li!

142
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,080
Wake up!

143
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:22,960
A'Li!

144
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,039
A'Li!

145
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,120
Red Heart,

146
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:35,080
as long as I, Shen Daozhi, am alive,

147
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,879
I will never let you hurt her.

148
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:43,879
Even if it costs me my life,

149
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:47,399
I will destroy you.

150
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:11,960
[You always believe]

151
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:14,600
[self-sacrifice is the right choice.]

152
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:16,960
[But if the premise is wrong,]

153
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,879
[how can there be a right answer?]

154
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:23,039
[Even if you choose wrong, so what?]

155
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,840
[I just want my beloved to live.]

156
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,840
No!

157
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:44,840
Shen Que!

158
00:12:54,039 --> 00:12:54,960
Li,

159
00:12:58,559 --> 00:12:59,799
it's okay now.

160
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,519
I...

161
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:15,279
I finally protected you.

162
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,240
After two lifetimes apart,

163
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:26,799
all I wanted

164
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,519
was to keep you safe.

165
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,679
Now,

166
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:35,240
I've done it.

167
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:44,120
If there's a next life,

168
00:13:49,679 --> 00:13:50,879
wait for me.

169
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,840
[I'll love you,]

170
00:13:59,000 --> 00:13:59,960
[protect you,]

171
00:14:01,879 --> 00:14:03,519
[and stay by your side.]

172
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,559
Daozhi!

173
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:43,440
Daozhi!

174
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,279
Shen Que!

175
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,240
Daozhi!

176
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,480
Daozhi!

177
00:15:24,039 --> 00:15:25,159
Daozhi!

178
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,799
I often dream.

179
00:15:30,799 --> 00:15:32,240
If I wake up

180
00:15:33,559 --> 00:15:35,360
to a world where demons

181
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,559
no more prejudice,

182
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,960
how wonderful that would be!

183
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,399
In that case,

184
00:15:46,559 --> 00:15:48,320
the sun would rise each day

185
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,720
to a world

186
00:15:51,639 --> 00:15:54,559
better than the last.

187
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,440
Even if we couldn't be together,

188
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,240
at worst,

189
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:03,960
we'd merely part ways.

190
00:16:06,159 --> 00:16:08,399
But in all these lifetimes with you,

191
00:16:09,559 --> 00:16:11,120
my wish has never come true.
